## IntRange.containsAll() method

Test if another range is completely within this range, inclusive.

**Signature:**

```typescript
containsAll(min: number, max: number): boolean;
```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  min | number | the minimum of the range to test |
|  max | number | the maximum of the range to test |

**Returns:**

boolean

`true` if `this.min <= min <= max <= this.max`
